high_descs: Turn left walk across the room and face the table beside the wall
Pick up the bread knife on the table
Move a little further on the table
Put the bread knife in the mug
Pick up the mug on the table
Turn to your right then cross the room  head to the shelf on  your left
Put the mug with bread knife on the top shelf
anns.task_desc: Put the mug with knife on the shelf

high_descs: Turn and go to the round table in the corner.
Pick up a butter knife on the round table.
Go to the round table in the corner.
Put the butter knife in the coffee cup on the round table.
Pick up the coffee cup on the round table.
Turn and go to the small table in the corner.
Put the coffee cup on the small table.
anns.task_desc: Move a coffee cup from the round table to the small table.

high_descs: Go to the round black table
Pick up a butterknife
Put the butterknife in a mug
Look at the mug
Pick up the mug from the table
Go to the small black table
Put the mug on the small black table
anns.task_desc: Move a mug with a butterknife in it to a small table
